article_title: Cigna Profit Grows, Though Top Line Misses
article_text:
Cigna Corp. logged better-than-expected earnings in its third quarter amid favorable medical and operating costs in the global health-care segment and customer growth.

Revenue, however, missed Wall Street expectations.
